localString.value: Touched by the evil deity, Iyachtu Xvim, this Hound has undergone a horrible transformation to become an agent of his infernal will.
Large, black hounds that prowl the night, these extra-planar creatures seek out any prey they can find. While not intelligent, they are cunning.
This artifact glows with a faint light and is also making a low humming sound. It bears arcane markings and has no obvious method of usage.
With their flaming wings and skull-like countenance, these demons are among the greatest and most feared of their kind.

A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur. Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
